Quote: He had lain for a month in a native hut visited by pubescent girls who supplied him with home comforts and African beer. ... `I had the dingbats for a while,' he said. ...@Well, when I had the dingbats there was a bloody great Negro's face an inch away from me all the time. It must have been the bad grog.'
